# 1.0.0

Scratchpad for everything we want to keep organized beyond the current README feature checklist.

Use this as the dumping ground for post-beta ideas, bigger 1.0 candidates, and random features we do not want to lose before they turn into a proper roadmap.

## Already implied outside the current README checklist

- GUI/mobile surfaces planned for 1.0
- Full parity for standard swap paths beyond the current Jupiter Ultra-first flow
- Broader strategy automation beyond today's queue jobs and scheduled routines
- Future alerting built off the structured runtime event bus
- Public-facing strategy engine once the current beta automation surface matures
- Any additional runtime/operator UX work that goes beyond the current v0.1.0 checklist

